data.title: Matthew 🇦🇺
data.content:
This is me arriving early at the Sydney Opera House before the crowds arrived to protest the gambling ads that the government forced the building to put on its sails tonight. Thousands turned up, to shine lights and cheer and boo, a great crowd. It was a lot of fun. People power!
